:"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Solicitar PL","guid":"oIaN01d-kIhl-8M-cZVp9w","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"• Iniciar tratamiento empírico","guid":"6MGJ0HIoIsjLa6LSy_LfRw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"• Recontrol en 2 semanas","guid":"knMbhMgSZxl05xpMVCGpCg","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"8","text":"• Resultado PL:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• VDRL en LCR: reactivo 1/5","guid":"FBLEZC5BA9_DCsHYFKe3Qg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"7","text":"Esquema de\\NTratamiento","guid":"NALSG_HLnbYayakXkrWT_A","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Penicilina G\\Nsódica:","guid":"Lw4FE7ALH-akuycjTGhk9g","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• 18-24 millones U/día IV (3-4 millones U cada 4 horas)","guid":"Y_cUJDDuTqgR7jbcGYXd4g","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"• Duración: 10-14 días","guid":"DRbbivKzchvzIjMCil27JQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"7","text":"Seguimiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Revaluar respuesta serológica a los 3, 6, 12, y 24 meses post-tratamiento","guid":"74KF755vEDubGMpwBWZIAA","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"• Control neurológico periódico","guid":"Cxgursau5djd-zeV9Q3TPA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"1","text":"Reacciones\\NAdversas a\\NPenicilinas","guid":"oRBG_EZE0QsvcO-b1eZNzg","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"1. Reacciones de\\Nhipersensibilidad:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Incidencia: comunes (3%-10%).","guid":"GPfk3qmsdXqpS6vwuVLwCg","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"QzxkGPOj36eH0GID5wlO8Q","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Exantema maculopapular.","guid":"iHOT6JPvF08zmE0hEe_png","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"• Urticaria.","guid":"mDSxN2V6ELCS0EBYY_n6SQ","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"• Angioedema.","guid":"lrID6otSjsc_f12l